FBIS4-36918 "drnes115_v_94005" FBIS-NES-94-115 Daily Report 11 Jun 1994 Pakistan Unknown Assailants Kill PPP Leader's Son Unknown Assailants Kill PPP Leader's Son BK1106162294 Islamabad Radio Pakistan Network in English 1600 GMT 11 Jun 94 BK1106162294 Islamabad Radio Pakistan Network English BFN [Text] Taufeeq Ahmed Sheikh was shot dead by some unknown assailants at Badami Bagh in Lahore today. He was son of the PPP [Pakistan People's Party] secretary general, Senator Sheikh Rafiq Ahmed. The assailants escaped after committing the murder. Investigations are in progress.
